name: Birddogs A.I. Art Mint Access Pass

metadata.name: A.I. Art Mint Access Pass
metadata.description:
I am excited to introduce my very own A.I. Art Mint Access Pass. With this pass, you will have the opportunity to mint pieces from my future collections, which will range in different themes and styles depending on the topic and style of A.I. art or photography that I am exploring. These projects combine my love for nostalgia, graphic design, and innovation to create unique A.I. pieces. Each piece is created using MidJourney and refined in Photoshop.

Who is Birddog? a graphic designer with over 10+ years of experience exploring AI as a tool and medium to create unique pieces of art in a style that I love. You can always reach out to me with any questions.

No other promises, just art for those that want it.
